---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Real Estate Accounting — CA Accounting"
  description="Outsourced accounting and tax planning for property managers, developers, investors, brokers and agents in California."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Real Estate</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          Outsourced accounting and tax strategy.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          Property managers, developers, investors, brokers and agents can save time when they take advantage of our outsourced accounting services and avoid tax problems with our tax planning strategies.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Real estate carries a unique tax and accounting profile. Our work for real estate clients spans bookkeeping, tax strategy, and entity reporting.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Accounting and bookkeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Traditional accounting and bookkeeping services to Glendale-area businesses.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Tax services</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Business tax return preparation and year-round tax planning to minimize tax liabilities.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">QuickBooks setup and training</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Setup, version selection, and staff training on QuickBooks.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Business formation</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Matching to the appropriate entity type plus startup guidance.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">IRS resolution</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Working on your behalf to resolve audits, tax liens, levies, and more.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Outsourced controllership and CFO</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Outsourced controller and CFO support for real estate businesses.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Cost segregation analysis</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Cost segregation analysis to identify accelerated depreciation opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">1031 exchanges</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Support for Section 1031 like-kind exchanges and tax deferral transactions.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Passive activity deductions</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Planning around passive activity deductions for real estate holdings.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Month-end closings</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Month-end closings, budgeting, and projections.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            From individual investors to growing portfolios.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Property managers, developers, investors, brokers, and agents across California. Each engagement is structured around how the work actually flows in your business.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Property managers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Mortgage brokers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Real estate agents</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Condo associations</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Commercial developers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Residential developers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Storage facilities</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Appraisers</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Ready to talk?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free initial consultation. We will review your current structure and tell you how we can help.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
